
Django-RefDB
============

Django-RefDB is a Web frontend for RefDB.  In other words, it is a reference
management tool, optimised for scientific references (papers/books).

It is in alpha stage, so don't use it productively.

See its homepage at <https://launchpad.net/django-refdb> and its documentation
at <http://www-users.rwth-aachen.de/torsten.bronger/django-refdb.html>.


